prerequisites

1. Install ffmpeg
sudo apt install ffmpeg

2. Install openai-whisper to run locally
pip install openai-whisper --break-system-packages
OR the below if system already have a conflicting whisper package
pip uninstall whisper -y --break-system-packages
pip uninstall openai-whisper -y --break-system-packages
pip install openai-whisper --break-system-packages
